column5: NEW Elevated Shipping Container Tiny House! Memory foam double bed, bamboo sheets, hardwood floors, Pottery Barn faux suede sofa. Kitchen with fridge, toaster oven, microwave, burner, & coffee maker. WiFi & HD-TV (streaming only - Netflix and HBONow provided) Decks with chairs off both living area & bedroom. Views of surrounding park land and owner's horse pasture. Located on 5 acres of privately owned land. Private driveway down to Onion Creek.
column8: Shipping Container Elevated Tiny House in S Austin
